'''Elisa Lasowski''' is a British actress.

She made her screen acting debut playing a prostitute in ''Eastern Promises''.

She plays [[Mirelle]] in ''[[Game of Thrones]]''. She was announced in the role on August 4 2012.<ref>[http://wicnet.tumblr.com/post/28731276130/blackfishblues-wicnet-casting-tidbit-i WiC.net Tumblr]</ref> She will appear in the [[Season 3|third season]].
